{"tid":2170504,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一年啦，藍罷買大boss係邊個？","createTime":"2020-08-23T10:09:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-23T10:54:31.000Z","uid":258041,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dba064b482b00f81679478cb7e886eb753a8d418","tid":2170504,"uid":258041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:09:00.000Z","msg":"黃幫襯藍罷買左一年<br />\n坦白講有時真係罷唔晒<br />\n盡力而為啦<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得邊間藍店勢力最大最難罷？<br />\n順便同大家loop多一次藍店個list<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我先<br />\n<br />\n我個人最成功杯葛：<br />\n美心集團（以前狂吃元氣/Starbucks/東海堂 )<br />\n吉野家（同上，曾經係最喜歡既快餐店）<br />\n優品360<br />\n<br />\n最失敗罷買：<br />\nikea, 惠康（怡和）<br />\n金拱門<br />\n四州集團（港版卡樂b）<br />\n<br />\n香港係加速成功前仲係打緊持久戰<br />\n希望呢個post可以同大家整理好藍店目標<br />\n罷緊既要繼續努力<br />\n罷失敗既一齊檢討<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dde5e333b435544ddc253f5e0e9c3edcd00038","tid":2170504,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:14:34.000Z","msg":"美心系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲係度"},{"pid":"63bff95087e9cf9b6e821ed6d227e7e30496eead","tid":2170504,"uid":139294,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:17:21.000Z","msg":"買少左老麥 可能幾個月先食一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美心元氣個啲就收皮啦 邊個食元氣我就屌柒佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e3d562fe1968883e7bc9c8db848520906d78e0","tid":2170504,"uid":181581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:18:54.000Z","msg":"成功得吉野家 360 <br />\n<br />\n失敗嘅仲有港鐵 一田"},{"pid":"7d1cf02e3d4afd5791497d7819d745312245cec4","tid":2170504,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:19:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aff797623493976eb030d611f15ccb5a6d256e48","tid":2170504,"uid":258041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2dde5e333b435544ddc253f5e0e9c3edcd00038","tid"